Added `ingest_clawdbot_jsonl()` to trajeval, enabling evaluation of real Clawdbot/OpenClaw session transcripts. This closes the loop between Phase 1 (clawdbot architecture study) and Phase 3 (building). The ingester maps assistant messages to `llm_call` steps, tool calls to `tool_call` steps with merged results, and bash executions to bash tool calls. Duration is computed from timestamps, tokens aggregated from usage data.

